# 📄 2. `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# Virtual environment
venv/
env/

# Jupyter Notebook
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# VS Code
.vscode/

# Mac
.DS_Store

# Environment variables
.env

# Model files (optional if large)
# churn_model.pkl
# scaler.pkl

# Logs
*.log